<plot>Nineveh is a transmedia drama of image, text and sound, a philosophical adventure integrated in an exalted and streaming operatic testimony. While exploring introspection, self-evaluation and intellectual-fulfilment with critical irony, amusing wit and challenging intelligence, it comments on the multi-dimensional existence of individual organisms and their alternative living style within today's trans-technological society.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?397174</url></doc>
